{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "04", "m": "06", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "02", "M": "34", "S": "02"}}, "news": [{"title": "Insomniacs and YoUnique Communication launches YouBeYou", "para": "Insomniacs and YoUnique Communication have launched YouBeYou, a new integrated communications ecosystem for India's real estate and infrastructure brands. This venture combines Insomniacs' digital marketing and tech expertise with YoUnique's PR and brand storytelling strengths. YouBeYou aims to offer a unified approach to enhance brand visibility, credibility, and long-term reputation for the sector.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/brand-connect-initiative/youbeyou-new-integrated-communications-ecosystem-for-real-estate-and-infrastructure-launched-by-insomniacs-and-younique-communication/131485775?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-2923553/131485775.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "brand-connect-initiative"}, {"title": "Propsoch raises $2 million in seed funding", "para": "Bengaluru-based Propsoch has secured USD 2 million in seed funding, with Athera Venture Partners, Sparrow Capital, and Vakil Group leading the round. This capital infusion will bolster research and advisory services, team expansion, and market growth. The company previously raised USD 600,000 in pre-seed funding.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/startups/propsoch-raises-2-million-in-seed-funding/131480289?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-31696/131480289.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "startups"}, {"title": "SC sets up expert panel on Aravalis, petitioners question its independence", "para": "The Supreme Court has formed a five-member high-powered committee to redefine the 'Aravali hills and ranges', dropping the controversial 100m height criterion. Thi